  "body": "From https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/issues/9935\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1162\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-04-21 at 15 59 39\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/2522130/233646254-713a5ead-fb90-41dc-b9f4-9ea2347dc745.png\">\r\n\r\nAdd event messages for:\r\n1) When contacts actually become mutual (not send, but accept CR)\r\n2) Removal of a contact\r\n\r\nEvents should be implemented on status-go side. Here is the example: https://github.com/status-im/status-go/pull/3414/files#diff-59d196f7f72de56c64ba2c559fcbb51762c418a22d2b83c59662b772a09b3c0aR779\r\n\r\nDesigns:\r\nhttps://www.figma.com/file/17fc13UBFvInrLgNUKJJg5/Kuba%E2%8E%9CDesktop?type=design&node-id=27345-528266\r\n",
